<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>A $79 white kitchen trolley from Kmart with multiple storage compartments is being praised by customers across Australia.</p>

<p>The trolley has a table top, drawer, wine rack, basket, side hooks and is built with wheels that can be locked into place.</p>

<p>Several shoppers shared images to the Kmart Homes, Ideas and Hacks Facebook group to reveal how the trolley has helped save kitchen space and add style to their homes. </p>

<p>The $79 Kmart trolley has a small table top, drawer, wine rack, basket and side hooks (pictured)</p>

